=== 國家隊 ===
安迪·卡路爾有資格代表[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]或[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]在國際賽上陣<small><ref> {{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11678_2412391,00.html |title=England & Scots chase Carroll |publisher=Sky Sports | date=2007-04-26 | accessdate=2009-10-12}}</ref></small>。他於2007年9月11日首次代表[[英格蘭19歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U-19]]出戰[[白俄羅斯19歲以下國家足球隊|白俄羅斯]]，在開賽後僅15分鐘先拔頭籌，協助球隊大勝4-0<small><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.chroniclelive.co.uk/nufc/newcastle-united-news/tm_headline=coach-8217-s-joy-at-carroll-8217-s-strike%26method=full%26objectid=19778448%26siteid=72703-name_page.html |title=Coach's Joy at Carroll's strike |publisher=ChronicleLive |date=2007-09-12 |accessdate=2009-10-12 |archive-date=2009-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090204010937/http://www.chroniclelive.co.uk/nufc/newcastle-united-news/tm_headline=coach-8217-s-joy-at-carroll-8217-s-strike%26method=full%26objectid=19778448%26siteid=72703-name_page.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。10月14日在備戰[[羅馬尼亞19歲以下國家足球隊|羅馬尼亞]]集訓期間，卡路爾、[[史葛·冼佳亞|史葛·冼佳亞]]及[[Ryan_Bertrand|比特蘭]]（Ryan Bertrand）因違反宵禁而被遣返所屬球會<small><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12010_2800655,00.html |title=England youngsters sent home |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2007-10-14 |accessdate=2009-10-12 |archive-date=2009-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090414061712/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12010_2800655,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

卡路爾於2009年8月5日首次獲徵召升上[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U-21]]<small><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.thefa.com/England/MensUnder-21Team/NewsAndFeatures/2009/SquadNamed_HollandGroningen.aspx |title=New campaign and new faces for Pearce |publisher=[[英格蘭足球總會|''thefa.com'']] |date=2009-08-05 |accessdate=2009-10-12 |archive-date=2010-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100201190514/http://www.thefa.com/England/MensUnder-21Team/NewsAndFeatures/2009/SquadNamed_HollandGroningen.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，8月11日作客[[友誼賽|友賽]][[荷蘭21歲以下國家足球隊|荷蘭]]首次以後補身份上陣<small><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.thefa.com/England/MensUnder-21Team/MatchCentre/2009/England%20v%20Holland/HollandvEngland_report.aspx |title=New-look Under-21s draw comfort in Holland |publisher=[[英格蘭足球總會|''thefa.com'']] |date=2009-08-11 |accessdate=2009-10-12 |archive-date=2010-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100224080058/http://www.thefa.com/England/MensUnder-21Team/MatchCentre/2009/England%20v%20Holland/HollandvEngland_report.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。他並沒有入選其後兩場作客的[[2011年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽|2011年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽]]外圍賽。直到10月9日返回主場對[[馬其頓21歲以下國家足球隊|馬其頓]]，卡路爾正選上陣，個人射入兩球兼有一個助攻，協助球隊大勝6-3<small><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8300248.stm |title=England U21 6-3 Macedonia U21 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-10-09 |accessdate=2009-10-12 |archive-date=2020-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023061919/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8300248.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

